      <div class="text-box">
        <h1>University of Macau</h1>
        <p>The University of Macau (UM) is a comprehensive higher education institution located in Macau, offering Bachelor's, Master's and Doctoral degree programmes in a wide range of fields. <br>Equipped with state-of-the-art teaching facilities and rich academic resources, the University is committed to nurturing outstanding human resources with international outlook and innovative capabilities to contribute to social and economic development.</p>
        <a href="" class="hero-btn">Visit Us To Know More</a>
