<!-----FACILITIES------>
<section class="facilities">
  <h1>Our Facilities</h1>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="facilities-col">
      <img src="../images/campusphoto-2-460x295.jpg">
      <h3>Library</h3>
      <p>The University of Macau Wu Yee Sun Library is a large seven-storey building with a collection of more than 12 million volumes/items, and provides a quality learning environment and facilities for students to enjoy reading and learning.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="facilities-col">
      <img src="../images/campusphoto-27-460x295.jpg">
      <h3>Administration Centre</h3>
      <p>The Administration Building of the University of Macau is a fully functional building providing office and administrative services. This modern building provides a comfortable working environment for staff and facilitates smooth communication and collaboration among various departments within the University to support the day-to-day operation and management of the University.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="facilities-col">
      <img src="../images/campusphoto-15-460x295.jpg">
      <h3>Science Research Building</h3>
      <p>The Research Building of the University of Macau is a modern building providing state-of-the-art research facilities and laboratories to provide students and teachers with a quality scientific research environment that promotes innovation and academic development.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

